{"tid":1970548,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"13人危殆  ICU警長繼續插喉","createTime":"2020-04-13T08:40:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T09:20:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1765e43893d7cc56554a5572f66ebc7645f82b3c","tid":1970548,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T08:40:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200413/77B5ISCACWKVPZ2CFUDKUSGSFE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200413%2F77B5ISCACWKVPZ2CFUDKUSGSFE%2F&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWTkC3bY0i4P88JjHF8GLL0M%3D&h=e125a867\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200413%2F77B5ISCACWKVPZ2CFUDKUSGSFE%2F&h=e042ca9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200413/77B5ISCACWKVPZ2CFUDKUSGSFE/</a><br />\n<br />\n13人危殆 <br />\nICU警長繼續插喉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200413/large/1586707519_b682.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200413%2Flarge%2F1586707519_b682.jpg&h=ef9e3816&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n確診警長上月曾參與太子站悼念活動的驅散行動。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港新增確診感染武漢肺炎個案有回落趨勢，但至今仍有637位患者留院，其中13人情況危殆，包括第854宗的46歲西九龍總區機動部隊男警長。醫管局總行政經理何婉霞表示，該名男警長仍需要插喉及用呼吸機。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局澄清無醫護確診<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：20警連續兩晚基隆查牌 凶員工熄爐<br />\n<br />\n何婉霞昨日於疫情簡報會公佈，截至昨日中午12時，仍有637位確診患者分別在14間醫院接受治療，其中13人危殆及8人嚴重，其餘616人情況穩定。除了該名男警長外，尚有第192宗、第312宗、第417宗、第427宗、第461宗、第498宗、第595宗、第698宗、第833宗、第840宗、第857宗及第856宗個案等情況危殆。而昨日有24位患者出院，至今累計有360位患者康復出院。<br />\n<br />\n有報道指，第428宗22歲女警曾向醫管局投訴，兩名抽血醫護人員誣衊她在抽血期間拒絕戴口罩，何婉霞稱，未有收到該宗投訴。另外又有傳聞指，有確診病人入院後提出叫外賣及遊戲機等不合理要求，何回應稱，明白病人住院期間有個人需要，院方會盡力配合，但她希望病人明白醫院提供的醫療服務要照顧不同人士需要，希望互相體諒。<br />\n<br />\n針對網傳有三名醫管局員工確診，包括屯門醫院急症科護士、博愛醫院社康護士及醫管局總辦事署員工一家人確診，何澄清該三名員工只是家人確診，屬於密切接觸者，而非確診者。對有指總辦事署的員工一家人確診，醫管局高層未有上報，只叫相關員工回家半日，何澄清該文職員工只有一位家人確診，需要入住隔離中心，又指局方已清潔消毒該員工的辦公室，並已通知同事，「之後會再加強同同事嘅溝通」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者謝明明"},{"pid":"fe2e6a55f43e36911823c914e95c67baac97f0b4","tid":1970548,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T08:41:39.000Z","msg":"大家集氣送上祝福同關心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />🙏🏻"},{"pid":"cde3122dc4725f357b878d70738b401f164a43f8","tid":1970548,"uid":194326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T08:41:55.000Z","msg":"標題成個咸濕片咁"},{"pid":"0350365e0ba6f53444193627dbdebd992beae786","tid":1970548,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T08:42:35.000Z","msg":"抵"},{"pid":"447ec8323da6a2a1820ed6f989b315278d8581d3","tid":1970548,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T08:42:36.000Z","msg":"3萬 thx"},{"pid":"b91cd6ecb104c90be2c4af396a3ff56683faeda4","tid":1970548,"uid":55458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T08:43:07.000Z","msg":"千其唔好死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcf4af3823faa525b612cd1d44be631f71a993c8","tid":1970548,"uid":112622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T08:43:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"282379960425245e15cb2bdbdc252f5f73259028","tid":1970548,"uid":112622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T08:44:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"56a3fb83354cb65d36c121a557a05cb82b542981","tid":1970548,"uid":44358,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T08:44:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">殘肺犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"fd785d03442ba18d11333886ef0019e4c96cac50","tid":1970548,"uid":271894,"lik